20288694647", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1942291290902667264/VZNzEahH_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Save America Guy", "username": "SaveAmericaGuy"}, "content": "As John Cornyn spreads pictures of him and Trump together to try to win his run-off against @KenPaxtonTX , remind the world of how Cornyn turned his back on Trump after 2020.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 0}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASG4uxz4X", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 26, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "hat", "id": 8465255, "raw_content": "If the Democrat Party Machine will cheat in the General Election- why would they not also cheat in the Primary Election?\n\nThere was a chance that a repulsive and unelectable candidate like Crockett would win the Primary. She would enter the General and get smoked. Her Primary opponent Tallarico has better odds and it makes sense Dem party leadership would prefer him in the General.\n\nSame goes for Bernie Sanders. Some think he was a sheepdog, but they treated him dirty in 2016 because he showed some potential and strength.\n\nIf the Dem establishment has a stockpile of dead voters  and  names of elderly that can be used on absentee ballots- why would they only use this weapon against Republicans in the General?\n\nLikewise, the two competing Primary candidates could simultaneously be cheating against one another using the same tactics.\n\nI think it's a good time to look into cleaning the voter rolls, tightening up mail in ballots and requiring voter ID.", "author": "Censorship_is4LOSERS", "created": 1772633956867, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Scot", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Jasmine Crockett is a ghetto piece of garbage but she may be right about voter fraud (Hear me out)", "last_comment_created": 1772638268067, "content": "<p>If the Democrat Party Machine will cheat in the General Election- why would they not also cheat in the Primary Election?</p>\n<p>There was a chance that a repulsive and unelectable candidate like Crockett would win the Primary. She would enter the General and get smoked. Her Primary opponent Tallarico has better odds and it makes sense Dem party leadership would prefer him in the General.</p>\n<p>Same goes for Bernie Sanders. Some think he was a sheepdog, but they treated him dirty in 2016 because he showed some potential and strength.</p>\n<p>If the Dem establishment has a stockpile of dead voters  and  names of elderly that can be used on absentee ballots- why would they only use this weapon against Republicans in the General?</p>\n<p>Likewise, the two competing Primary candidates could simultaneously be cheating against one another using the same tactics.</p>\n<p>I think it's a good time to look into cleaning the voter rolls, tightening up mail in ballots and requiring voter ID.</p>\n", "score_down": 1, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 27, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "SAVE AMERICA", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2029007573983068256", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASG4uyWpx", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 20, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8465405, "raw_content": "", "author": "votedforthe45th", "created": 1772639058466, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDona